  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN315-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. neṭumāṉañciyai oḷavaiyār
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN315">
<l>uṭaiya ṉāyi ṉuṇṇavum vallaṉ</l>
<l>kaṭavar mītu mirappōrk kīyu</l>
<l>maṭavar makiḻtuṇai neṭumā ṉañci</l>
<l>yilliṟaic cerīiya ñelikōl pōlat</l>
<l>tōṉṟā tirukkavum vallaṉ maṟṟataṉ</l>
<l>kāṉṟupaṭu kaṉaiyeri pōlat</l>
<l>tōṉṟavum vallaṉṟāṉ ṟōṉṟuṅ kālē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If he possesses [something], he is capable also of eating.</l>
<l>He gives to mendicants even over those to whom he has a duty.</l>
<l>He is the companion in delight of youthful [women], Neṭumāṉañci.</l>
<l>Like a kindling stick tucked away in the eave of the house</l>
<l>he is capable of sitting without appearing. Then again, like</l>
<l>the intense flame that shoots forth from that</l>
<l>he is also capable of appearing, at the time he appears.  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
